<br>
The fire pet after 50 lost all of the 50- advantages it had (good melee, great damage shield, great overall DPS).<br>
<br>
Given the level of the pet, it is reasonable for a 50+ fire pet to cast nukes that a level 29-34 wizard may cast (such as Thunder Strike, Inferno Shock, Ice Shock, etc).  Maybe it will raise the DPS above other pets, but it having such low hitpoint (and possibly lower damage mitigation as many wizards can attest) will still keep this pet in the group situation and not as a primary tank.<br>
